name: Skaiwater
description: '''Tyler Ryan Lee Jordan Brooks''', (born 31 August 2000), known professionally as '''Skaiwater''' (previously known as '''Young Skai'''), is a British [[rapper]] and record producer from [[Nottingham]]. Brooks first rose to commercial fame on [[TikTok]] with the release of their{{efn|name=gender}} track, "#miles", as well as its accompanied remix featuring [[Lil Uzi Vert]].
